{"tid":1440092,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍係主要幹道","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:38:23.000Z","uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7866ab9a6c31d32c0444bceba8b1da695d02297b","tid":1440092,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"利伸：本身住大圍，基本上地頭蟲。<br />\n大圍迴旋處係主要幹道，<br />\n大圍出黎一定係用迴旋處，<br />\n基本上出九龍就係靠果度。<br />\n獅子山隧道來回，顯徑來回，新翠果邊來回，部分通往沙田新城市道路，<br />\n乃至馬鞍山出黎都係用迴旋處！<br />\n<br />\n大埔行完見到好多手足去大圍真心感動，<br />\n抱歉凈係得字冇圖，<br />\n而且果度四通八達，好多地方走。<br />\n本身住大圍既不妨一齊過黎。<br />\n游擊必勝！光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"eeb0bba79fb433646006be25e269f72be02a6aca","tid":1440092,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"@1832 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=d35c3200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsq1nFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqsq1nFE.png&h=0dad253f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"36f70e1deba8eb075f5a04244704e4fb6a8f6faf","tid":1440092,"uid":142203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"封晒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7yKksE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7yKksE.jpg&h=c61eeb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwBDpUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwBDpUn.jpg&h=9c992f31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3MqQf05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3MqQf05.jpg&h=419202e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b55fbe7